OL,3,CConcern for hundreds of jobs at
OL,4,CBrace's Bakery
OL,6,FHundreds of staff at Brace's Bakery in
OL,7,FNewport are nervously waiting to learn
OL,8,Fif their jobs are secure following
OL,9,Frecent financial pressures at the
OL,10,Fcompany.
OL,12,FThe site at Pen-y-Fan industrial
OL,13,Festate, which employs around 250
OL,14,Fworkers, is said to be under threat
OL,15,Funless a new buyer is found.
OL,17,FEmployees who did not want to be named
OL,18,Fhave also said there has been recent
OL,19,Fissues where staff were not paid the
OL,20,Ffull amount they were owed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/2
