OL,3,CConcern for hundreds of jobs at
OL,4,CBrace's Bakery
OL,6,FIn a statement to ITV News, director
OL,7,FJonathan Brace said:
OL,9,F'As you are aware Brace's have been
OL,10,Ffacing difficult headwinds over the
OL,11,Flast few months in a challenging
OL,12,Fmarket.
OL,14,F'We are in talks with a potential
OL,15,Fbuyer & we expect to be able to update
OL,16,Fyou further within 24 to 48hrs.
OL,18,F'Safeguarding the jobs of our loyal
OL,19,Fworkforce is our primary objective to
OL,20,Fensure our quality range of products
OL,21,Fremain available for years to come.'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/2
